BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Marin Jcc": "https://www.marinjcc.org/event/shabbat-shmooze-4/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:marin_jcc
X-SOURCE:Marin Jcc
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260313T160000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260313T171500
DTSTAMP:20260312T191906
CREATED:20260225T202058Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260225T202800Z
UID:10001685-1773417600-1773422100@www.marinjcc.org
SUMMARY:Shabbat Shmooze
DESCRIPTION:Please join us in the JCC lobby to welcome in Shabbat\, where we will be joined by Covenant Winery proprietor Jodie Morgan and General Manager Zoe Morgan-Koelewijn for a wine tasting! Enjoy the live French cafe music of Bistro Mustache. Light snacks will be provided. \n  \n \n  \nCovenant Winery is an urban winery located in Berkeley. We source grapes grown in some of the finest vineyards in California and Israel\, places where we enjoy a historical and personal connection to the land. As such\, we strive to harness quality in the bottle that reflects the unique aspects of the land and the vines we are privileged to work with. Our winemaking techniques highlight what the land gives us naturally. All our wines are certified kosher and are naturally vegan. Discover our world through our wines! www.covenantwines.com \n  \nWe will gather every 2nd Friday\, monthly.  \n  \nFree event! All are welcome. No registration\, just drop-in! 
URL:https://www.marinjcc.org/event/shabbat-shmooze-4/
LOCATION:Osher Marin JCC\, 200 North San Pedro Road\, San Rafael\, CA\, 94903\, United States
CATEGORIES:Jewish Life
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://www.marinjcc.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/1400x1080-1.png
END:VEVENT
