X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Meetup Jewish Singles": "https://www.meetup.com/bay-area-jewish-singles-havurah/events/313748141/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:meetup_jewish_singles
X-SOURCE:Meetup Jewish Singles
UID:event_313748141@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260313T021925Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260313T183000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260313T213000
SUMMARY:Shabbat Dinner
DESCRIPTION:Bay Area Jewish Singles Havurah\nWe welcome you to join us for our Shabbat dinner on March 13\, 2026. This will be held in San jose\, at the home of one of our group members. The address will be shared closer to the date of the event.\n\nAttendance is limited to 20 individuals.\n\nYou're welcome to invite your single Jewish friends. Nevertheless\, we request that your guests register for the event on the meetup site directly. Thus\, the guest feature is disabled for this event.\n\nWe are asking for a donation of $3 per person to offset the cost of the MeetUp fees ( to be paid every 6 months by David and me).\n\nFood: This will be a potluck dinner\, please bring either a side or main dish\, a salad or dessert. Please bring a dish large enough to feed 8-10 people. You are welcome to bring a bottle of wine as well\, if you would like. Please no pork\, bacon\, shellfish (shrimp\, clams etc.) nor dishes that mix both milk products and meat ( ie meat lasagna\, Cosco premade sandwiches w/ cold cuts and cheese ). Two separate platters- one with meats/ cold cuts\, and another platter with cheese is fine.\n\nWe will provide plates\, cups\, cutlery and non-alcoholic drinks. The stove\, microwave and oven will be available for you to reheat your dish. Nevertheless\, due to time constraints\, please bring the dish already prepared. Please write what you will bring in the comments section so that others can see.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/bay-area-jewish-singles-havurah/events/313748141/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260311T202724Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260311T202724Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/8/1/e/3/600_505833251.jpeg
END:VEVENT
