BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Meetup Mountain Jew": "https://www.meetup.com/mountain-jew/events/313622189/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:meetup_mountain_jew
X-SOURCE:Meetup Mountain Jew
UID:event_313622189@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260313T021925Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260313T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260313T210000
SUMMARY:MHWOW - Sweet & Sour Shabbat
DESCRIPTION:Mountain Jew\n🔒 Want to attend? This Meetup won't show location or tickets — full access is in the "About Mountain Jew" section below.\nLet's wok and roll! :) Jacob and I would love to have you join us for Sweet & Sour Shabbat. Let's enjoy some classic American-Chinese dishes together -- think fried rice\, spring rolls\, soups\, noodles\, vegetable dishes\, tofu\, and sweet and sour chicken.\nThis meal will be a Kosher Meat meal. Even with the generous support of OneTable and MHWOW\, meat is expensive. If you are interested and able to help contribute to the purchase of kosher meat\, please indicate so when you RSVP. I would love to make a couple chicken dishes. This is greatly appreciated!!\nCandle lighting time: 6:55pm (would love to have you join)\nWe will start songs\, blessings\, and dinner at 7:30pm.\nParking is available on the street and the first floor of the parking deck.\nMeet us by the pool gate -- dinner in the clubhouse.\nSee you soon! :)\n——————————————————\n✡️ About Mountain Jew\nMountain Jew is a community exclusively for Jewish young professionals in the Bay Area. Jewish people make up less than 0.2% of the world's population\, so having spaces like this to connect with one another is incredibly meaningful — we kindly ask that this be respected.\nThis is where people don't just show up to events — they actually meet\, connect\, and build real friendships. From hikes to dinners to social gatherings\, it's a community that's active\, welcoming\, and easy to plug into.For the comfort and safety of our members\, full event details (including exact locations) are shared only with verified MJ members.\n➡️ Join us: https://mountainjew.org\nGet verified to access the full calendar\, RSVP to events\, and join the WhatsApp community.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/mountain-jew/events/313622189/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260303T201551Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260303T201551Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/3/4/5/a/600_532933402.jpeg
END:VEVENT
