SUMMARY:Application: SF Sephardic Fellowship
DESCRIPTION:JIMENA is excited to announce our SF Fellowship\, which brings together communal professionals across sectors working in Jewish Institutions\, communities\, etc.\, who are committed to strengthening Sephardic\, Mizrahi and Israeli engagement within their institutions and communities. \nThrough immersive learning\, including walking tours of Sephardic San Francisco\, sessions with local leaders and professionals\, and applied study of our demographic research\, fellows will build the skills and insight needed to develop more inclusive programs\, and informed policies. \nThe fellowship will launch in person on April 16th at the Jewish Federation of San Francisco\, followed by six additional sessions held every other week\, alternating between in-person and online formats. If you have any questions\, please don’t hesitate to contact me.
URL:https://jewishfed.org/event/application-sf-sephardic-fellowship/
