 for our signature monthly gathering—a night of good food\, great company\, 
 and a relaxed\, egalitarian Shabbat atmosphere.</p><p>Whether you’re a regu
 lar or a first-timer\, if you’re in your <b>mid-20s to 40-ish</b>\, we’d lo
 ve to have you at the table. No experience necessary!</p><h3><b>The Details
 </b></h3><ul><li><p><b>Location:</b> Congregation Beth Sholom</p></li><li><
 p><b>Time:</b> <b>7:00 PM</b> for dinner <i>(Services at 6:00 p.m. in the C
 hapel)</i></p></li><li><b>Cost:</b> Free for CBS Members | $10 for Guests<p
 ></p></li></ul><h3><b><u><u><a href="https://cbssf.shulcloud.com/form/young
 ish-shabbat-3/20/26.html">Register Here! </a></u></u></b></h3><p><b>RSVP re
 quired by Thursday\, March 19th.</b> Grab your spot! Once we hit capacity\,
  we will move to a waitlist.</p>
