DESCRIPTION:What’s all this fuss about the Count of Omer? Counting the Omer
  with Marilyn Heiss<br>Sunday\, March 22nd at 6pm <br><br>Every year\, Jewi
 sh tradition asks us to count forty-nine days — one by one — from Pesach to
  Shavuot\, with no reason given. Join us as we explore the origins and evol
 ving rituals of Sefirat HaOmer\, and pick up practical materials to make yo
 ur daily count more meaningful this year. <br><br><a href="https://us02web.
 zoom.us/j/82290828821">https://us02web.zoom.us/j/82290828821</a><br>Meeting
