 ber 13<br>January 24<br>February 28<br>March 28</h4><p>Whether you are new 
 to Judaism or have been sitting in services for years and would like a refr
 esher\, you are welcome! Join Jonathan Bayer\, CBS Music Specialist and lov
 er of Torah and Jewish texts\, to dive deeper into our most foundational pr
 ayers. Each session will focus on one prayer: the whats\, hows and whys. Jo
 in us for one class or all five!</p><p><em>No registration necessary\, walk
 -ins welcome.</em></p>
