SUMMARY:Jewish Meditation Group
DESCRIPTION:Come join us for a monthly Jewish Meditation Group\, led by Larry and Diane Yermack. \nMeets monthly on the last Monday of each month. No registration needed\, just drop-in! \n\n\n\nIn this group you will discover the joy and impact of developing an ongoing meditation practice\, led by Larry and Diane Yermack. It is also an opportunity to grow an open\, compassionate attentiveness to the world around you. Join us whether you’re new to meditation or it’s been a long-term practice of yours.
URL:https://www.marinjcc.org/event/jewish-meditation-group-4-3-2/2026-03-30/
LOCATION:JCC 2nd Floor Yoga Studio\, 200 N. San Pedro Rd.\, San Rafael\, 94903\, United States
CATEGORIES:Jewish Life
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.marinjcc.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Meditation.jpg
END:VEVENT
