 abbis felt would help us to prepare for "receiving the Torah" on Shavuot!<b
 r><br>Join us!<br>Saturdays at 1pm<br>April 11\, 18 and 25<br>May 2\, 9 and
  16<br><br><a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1OyBDauBt1d05XKno23qF2s
 Y45tnJ38k05HHK8xKhdd8/viewform?edit_requested=true">Register here</a><br><b
 r>This offering will be a mix of lay and clergy lead.<br><br>Some materials
  may be sent ahead of time\, so please check your email in advance of Shabb
 at.<br><br>Questions? Contact CBS member: Joachim Steinberg\, jbsteinberg@g
 mail.com
