SUMMARY:Jewish Arts & Bookfest
DESCRIPTION:Join the Magnes for the second annual Jewish Arts & BookFest in celebration of Jewish American Heritage Month. \nIn the Magnes tradition of incubating Jewish cultural events\, the Arts & Bookfest will bring together authors and artists for panel discussions\, workshops\, readings\, teen programs\, and performances that showcase the Jewish experience through art\, culture\, and storytelling. \nSunday\, May 3\, 2026\nIn person at the Magnes Collection of Jewish Art and Life\, 2121 Allston Way\, Berkeley\, CA \nJewish Arts & Bookfest Website \nFor more information\, please reach out to magnesprograms@berkeley.edu. \nIf you have any questions about accessibility or require accommodations to participate in this event\, please contact us at magnes@berkeley.edu or call us at (510) 643-2526 with as much advance notice as possible.
